        "rich_text_PpMKK8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Although the recent trend feels modern, Toi et Moi rings have a long history.</p><p>One of the most famous examples belonged to Jacqueline Kennedy, whose engagement ring featured a diamond and an emerald placed together.</p><p>The combination of these stones created a striking contrast while maintaining elegance.</p><p>This historic ring helped establish the idea that two stones could represent two individuals within one design.</p><p>Even today, many Toi et Moi rings follow a similar concept by combining different gemstones or diamond shapes.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
