        "rich_text_PQPfdj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Celebrity Rings Made the Style Popular Again",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Celebrity Rings Made the Style Popular Again</h2><p>Celebrity engagements often influence jewellery trends, and Toi et Moi rings are no exception.</p><p>What made these rings stand out was not just their appearance, but also their meaning.</p><p>The design reflects:</p><p>1.] Partnership between two people<br/><br/>2.] Individuality within a relationship<br/><br/>3.] Balance between two different elements<br/><br/>As more celebrities chose this style, it encouraged couples to explore rings that felt more personal than traditional solitaire designs.</p>",
            "custom_id": "rings-made",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_HFQYLM": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Couples Are Choosing Toi et Moi Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Couples Are Choosing Toi et Moi Rings</h2><p>Beyond celebrity influence, the Toi et Moi ring appeals to couples who want something meaningful and slightly unconventional.</p><p>Instead of focusing on one stone, the design highlights two stones sharing the spotlight.</p><p>Some couples choose:</p><p>1.] Two different diamond shapes<br/><br/>2.] A diamond paired with a coloured gemstone<br/><br/>3.] Birthstones representing each partner<br/><br/>Designs like the Portuguese Toi et Moi Ring, Hexa & Pear Diamond Toi et Moi Ring, and Marquise & Round Toi et Moi Ring from Lucira show how this concept can be interpreted in many different ways.</p><p>The result is a ring that feels personal and symbolic.</p>",
            "custom_id": "modern",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_tmWELN": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lucira’s Take on the Toi et Moi Design At Lucira Jewelry, Toi et Moi rings are crafted to celebrate ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lucira’s Take on the Toi et Moi Design</h2><p>At Lucira Jewelry, Toi et Moi rings are crafted to celebrate the idea of two unique stones coming together in harmony.</p><p>Each design balances shape, proportion, and brilliance so that both stones complement each other naturally. Lucira rings feature IGI-certified lab-grown diamonds, offering modern craftsmanship while maintaining ethical sourcing.</p><p>From classic diamond pairings to gemstone combinations, Lucira’s collection reflects the timeless meaning behind the Toi et Moi style.</p>",
            "custom_id": "take-on",
